videos.description: Gabe Brown rises up to the rim and throws down a big slam in an effort to clean up a pair of misses.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (MSU's Brown cleans up with powerful dunk) 2020/1/29

videos.headline: MSU's Brown cleans up with powerful dunk

videos.description: Julius Marble takes advantage of a Northwestern turnover, slamming down a rim-rocking jam on the other end but receives a technical foul for hanging on the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marble's monster slam pumps up the crowd) 2020/1/29

videos.headline: Marble's monster slam pumps up the crowd

videos.description: Foster Loyer pulls up from deep to sink his fourth triple on the night, the 12th overall as a team, in Michigan State's blowout win vs. Northwestern.
videos.headline: Loyer drains Michigan State's 12th 3-pointer
